THIS WEEKEND?

43:59.845 --> 44:02.056
YEAH.

44:02.139 --> 44:05.059
YEAH. AND ONE OF THOSE,
UH, DANGLING THINGS?

44:05.142 --> 44:06.226
MOBILE.

44:06.310 --> 44:07.561
THAT'S IT.

44:07.645 --> 44:09.730
